cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.SY, cs.RO 

The paper discusses reinforcement learning and probabilistic modeling, which are core topics in machine learning and artificial intelligence. The focus on active inference and its implementation suggests a strong connection to the subfield of machine learning known as active learning, which is often categorized under cs.LG. The paper also discusses exploration and sample efficiency, which are important topics in reinforcement learning and optimization, suggesting connections to cs.AI, cs.NE, and cs.SY. Finally, the paper presents results on a high-dimensional task, which suggests connections to robotics and control, and thus cs.RO.
